{"tid":1663140,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家幫手拉黑呢條深藍","createTime":"2019-10-19T08:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T08:31:55.000Z","uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb711cea486bf9c28546cc86ec145defe2ca1474","tid":1663140,"uid":96694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:30:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZroQSvY-Lh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZroQSvY-Lh8&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=2a82d283\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZroQSvY-Lh8</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該路過手足麻煩檢舉一下啦<br />\n咁多個月以黎<br />\n一直拉黑所有示威者既行為<br />\n抹黑我地所做嘅一切<br />\n<br />\n佢呢條片  大家都知係事實<br />\n但發生呢d事既前因後果 又唔會同大家交代清楚<br />\n只係識得遊花園  拉攏大陸一班網民幫佢大肆宣傳<br />\n<br />\n到底呢一刻 我地所做既野 仲可以唔理解 唔明白咩<br />\n我地都愛國愛港    但唔愛中共 ok?"},{"pid":"9fd00835e419fd4099784aad173b2df99cea3b1e","tid":1663140,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"明天見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSJhsF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSJhsF.png&h=a75a6d4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3111a6b45c863c9b775530723a51b29116add3e8","tid":1663140,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:30:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"957c31ba5086f90a31c02b9bbb083c472aa64d38","tid":1663140,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:30:31.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>全日 全民宣傳日</strong></span> <br />\n- 宣傳1020民陣大遊行<br />\n日期：10月20日<br />\n時間： 1330 <br />\n地點：梳士巴利花園<br />\n[ 各區宣傳，嗌口號，貼文宣，Airdrop ]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1900 - 2030 國際人道救援祈禱會</strong></span><br />\n- 